[normal]4.4.3
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Where employers do not sufficiently train managers in techniques for advertising and int
[normal]erviewing women, gender imbalances proliferate
[normal];
[normal]4.4.4
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Lack of 
[normal]u
[normal]nconscious 
[normal]b
[normal]ias training for hiring managers sets opinion in favour of the controlling group, which at this time in 
[normal]our
[normal] sector is 
[normal]overwhelmingly 
[normal]male. 
[normal]However, uptake and implementation 
[normal]of this type 
[normal]of education is sporadic
[normal] and inconsistent
