[normal]  
[normal]4.4.5
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The IT industry requires many 
[normal]business 
[normal]skills, and recruit
[normal]ing
[normal] graduates with business skills and MBA qualifications can be benefi
[normal]cial
[normal] where there are declining numbers of graduates from pure ICT courses.  Anecdotally many individuals come to IT roles from different starting points
