[normal]4.4.6
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Dissemination of best practice on recruitment policies to make IT employers the companies of choice for women 
[normal]is
[normal] essential to ensure that the industry acquires the skills at both graduate and skilled practitioner levels
